**【数据提取与转换：Cron Jobs】**

**工具链：** read_file → python3 -c json → bash

1. 读取 cron/jobs.json
$ cat ~/.hermes/cron/jobs.json | python3 -c "import sys,json; j=json.load(sys.stdin); [print(f'{job[\"id\"]}: {job[\"name\"]} @ {job.get(\"schedule\",\"?\")}') for job in j['jobs']]"

$ cat ~/.hermes/cron/jobs.json | python3 -c "
import sys,json;
j=json.load(sys.stdin);
print(f'{len(j[\"jobs\"])} jobs');
from datetime import datetime, timezone;
now = datetime.now(timezone.utc).timestamp();
for job in j['jobs']:
    name = job.get('name','?')
    schedule = job.get('schedule','?')
    last = job.get('last_run_at','')
    print(f'  {name}: schedule={schedule}, last_run={last}')"

